       <a name="fonts" class="hidden"><big> Fonts </big></a>
       <ul>
         <li><a href="http://www.tldp.org/HOWTO/Font-HOWTO/">TTF on Linux HOWTO</a>
         <li><a href="http://www.microsoft.com/typography/unicode/cs.htm">Charset info</a> From Microsoft.
         <li><a href="http://rcum.uni-mb.si/local/fontfaq/cf_1.htm">comp.fonts</a> The home page is gone, but the <a href="http://nwalsh.com/comp.fonts/FAQ/index.html">FAQ</a>
